channel.title: Ronnie VS Craig
channel.description:
[center][img]http://profile.ak.fbcdn.net/hprofile-ak-snc4/23303_112239648811907_2818_n.jpg[/img]
Hey guys.
Well, the other day I got the song [url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kK1LZRwzAts&feature=related]Make Up[/url] by Escape the Fate when Ronnie was still singer. More exactly it was the Situations EP. I was looking at the comments and I saw multiple people saying "Yay for Craig!" and "Yay for Ronnie!". I just am curious, who do you think is better?
I think Ronnie is 10x better than Craig in singing and writing songs. I also just got Ronnies new album and it beats the fuck out of the latest Escape the Fate album xD
So tell me what you think Mopar![/center]
